These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There 2 different types of food: onion, orange
2 different pets are kept: hamster, pony
1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
2. the person eating onion is not to the right of the owner of the pony##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Food        | onion   | orange   |
| Pet   | pony | hamster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, scientist
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the scientist##8
2. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the scientist##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Job   | scientist | designer   |
| Sport      | lacrosse | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, russian
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, r&b
1. the argentine is not to the left of the fan of r&b##8
2. the russian is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Nationality          | russian | argentine |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | r&b     |

